QUETZAL
The Coalescence Template Library

◆ Tree() [3/6]

template<typename CellT >
quetzal::coalescence::Tree< CellT >::Tree ( CellT &&  cell)
noexcept

Constructor with data move.

Parameters
cellthe value of the tree cell
Remarks
CellT must be move constructible.

Example

#include "assert.h"
#include <iostream>
int main(){
using quetzal::coalescence::Tree;
using std::string;
// initialization by default constructor
Tree<int> a;
Tree<int> b;
Tree<int> c;
// assignment by copy assignment operator
a = b;
// assignment by move assignment operator
c = std::move(b); // b should not be used anymore !
int cell = 12;
// initialization copying cell
Tree<int> d(cell);
// initialization moving cell
Tree<int> e(std::move(cell)); // cell should not be used anymore !
std::cout << "done" << std::endl;
return 0;
}
